column5: Our group is heading up to lake Minnitaki this Friday. Does anybody have any advice or fishing reports? We will be staying on Neepawa Island. Can't wait to get out on the lake! Thanks in advance!

Sorry I didn't see your post earlier, how was your trip ?Did you use Kai's boats, please let us know how the trip was.Heading up next year, couldn't make it this year. It will be my third trip to Neepawa Island.Thanks!!!
